acme.name: Vincent Desk
acme.description: Rectangular Computer Desk Compact Workstation Storage: Pull-Out Keyboard (Size: 27" x 11"), Open Compartment (Metal Shelf, Fixed) Recommended Monitor: 32" Flat Panel Screen Clear Glass Top (5mm Clear, 29" x 24") Metal Frame & Shelf Caster Wheels Included
acme.short_description: The Vincent computer desk offers a compact, sleek and contemporary design. This workstation is crafted in metal pewter finish with clear glass top. Features pull-out metal keyboard tray and bottom metal shelf.
